6000|$|... "Well," [...] said Reggie, drowsily, [...] "there {{are several}} ways of bidding, you know. You can shout, or you can nod, or you can twiddle your fingers--" [...] The effort of {{concentration}} {{was too much for}} him. <b>He</b> <b>leaned</b> <b>back</b> limply <b>in</b> his chair. [...] "I'll tell you what. I've nothing to do this afternoon. I'll come with you and show you." ...|$|R
