6000|$|However, {{this evening}} was an exception. Generally we talked of the West, of cattle ranching, of {{trailing}} {{and of the}} splendid types of pioneers who were about to vanish from the earth. One night as we sat at dinner in his house, <b>he</b> suddenly <b>leaned</b> <b>back</b> <b>in</b> his chair and {{said with a smile}} [...] "I can't tell you how I enjoy having a man at my table who knows the difference between a parfleche and an aparejo." ...|$|R
